    "description": "<strong>SpellBit</strong> is a fast-paced mini battle royale game designed for 12 players per match. It draws major inspiration from games like Fortnite and Spellbreak, offering a smaller scale experience with even more excitement!<br><br>Unleash <strong>devastating spells</strong> and manipulate the very fabric of reality to outwit and overpower your opponents. Engage in <strong>fast-paced</strong>, strategic combat, combining precise spellcasting with cunning tactics to emerge victorious.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Engage in <strong>intense fights</strong> against other mages!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133570/extras/a269b2b21d904e40702588c29af42e10.poster.avif?t=1724248877\" width=598 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133570/extras/a269b2b21d904e40702588c29af42e10.webm?t=1724248877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133570/extras/a269b2b21d904e40702588c29af42e10.mp4?t=1724248877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Master your <strong>flying</strong> skills!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133570/extras/bdf0fe2488743ad0918b846b5c2c4f43.poster.avif?t=1724248877\" width=598 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133570/extras/bdf0fe2488743ad0918b846b5c2c4f43.webm?t=1724248877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133570/extras/bdf0fe2488743ad0918b846b5c2c4f43.mp4?t=1724248877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Customize your mage, choosing from a <strong>diverse range of spell schools</strong> and unlocking <strong>unique characters</strong>.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133570/extras/f3358ba7dbf2ad66883eda40d98dfe18.avif?t=1724248877\" width=598 height=334 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Find <strong>epic loot</strong> to help you win battles!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133570/extras/ae8256446a9f44266d2246de96f77784.poster.avif?t=1724248877\" width=598 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133570/extras/ae8256446a9f44266d2246de96f77784.webm?t=1724248877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133570/extras/ae8256446a9f44266d2246de96f77784.mp4?t=1724248877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
